The '''Quarry penal colony''' was a [[Gungan/Legends|Gungan]] prison colony. Hard labor was apparently included as part of the penal system there. After [[Jar Jar Binks/Legends|Jar Jar Binks]] inadvertently allowed half of the animals to escape from the [[Otoh Gunga/Legends|Otoh Gunga]] [[Otoh Gunga Zoological Research Facility|zoo]], [[Boss/Legends|Boss]] [[Rugor Nass/Legends|Rugor Nass]] sentenced him to six months hard labor at the Quarry penal colony, although the sentence was later commuted.

